---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import logo from "../../public/imgs/primært_logo_lyserød.svg";
---

<section class="footer">
  <div>
    <Image src={logo} alt="Logo" class="footer-logo" />
    <p>Vi er en frivillig forening som hjælper unge talenter i den danske reklame- og kommunikationsbranche med at netværke, udvikle dit portfolio og få foden indenfor i den kreative branche.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-right">
    <div>
      <h3>Socials</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/youngcreativesdk?locale=da_DK">Facebook</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/youngcreativesdenmark/">Instagram</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div><h3>Telefon</h3><ul><li>60 91 43 26</li></ul></div>
    <div>
      <h3>Adresse</h3><ul>
        <li>Jacob Cameron Brook</li>
        <li>Landskronagade 27, st.,</li>
        <li>2100 København Ø</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    background-color: var(--color-blå);
    height: auto;
  }

  li {
    list-style: none;
  }
  a {
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  p,
  h3,
  li,
  a {
    color: var(--color-lyserød);
    max-width: 100%;
    max-height: 200px;
    font-size: small;
  }
  li {
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: xx-small;
  }
  h3 {
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  p {
    max-width: 300px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: xx-small;
    padding-left: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .footer-logo {
    width: 200px;
    max-width: 90%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    padding-bottom: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-left: 3rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
  }
  .footer-right {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .footer-right {
    padding: 1rem 3rem;
  }
  @media screen and (width >= 768px) {
    .footer-logo {
      width: 280px;
      max-width: 90%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      padding-bottom: 0;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    p,
    h3,
    li,
    a {
      color: var(--color-lyserød);
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    section {
      padding: 6rem 4rem;
    }
    .footer {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      width: 280px;
      max-width: 90%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      padding-bottom: 0;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    p {
      max-width: 450px;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: medium;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: large;
    }
    li,
    li a {
      font-weight: 200;
      font-size: medium;
    }
  }
</style>
